---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Pricing — Voq"
  description="Voq reads any webpage aloud in a natural-sounding AI voice, free every day, inside a structured panel you can skip around in. Remove the daily limit for $2/mo as a founding member — locked in before the price rises to $5/mo."
>
<div class="container">
<main class="pricing-page">

  <section class="hero">
    <span class="eyebrow">turn any page into something you can listen to</span>
    <h1>Voq reads the web to you.<br/>Free every day. <em>No limit</em> for $2/mo.</h1>
    <p class="sub">
      Highlight text or open the panel and Voq reads it aloud in a natural,
      human-sounding AI voice — not the robotic default your browser ships with.
      It opens in a structured panel too, so you can skip straight to the section
      you want instead of listening start to finish. All of that's free, every
      single day, up to a daily listening budget. Want no daily cap at all? Lock
      in the founding rate before it goes up.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="tiers">
    <div class="tier">
      <span class="tag">always free</span>
      <h2>$0<span>/mo</span></h2>
      <p class="who">Natural AI voice, every day, up to a daily limit</p>
    </div>
    <div class="tier featured">
      <span class="tag">founding rate</span>
      <h2>$2<span>/mo</span></h2>
      <p class="who">No daily limit, ever — while you stay subscribed</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="subscribe-cta">
    <a
      class="subscribe-btn"
      href="https://voq-tts.julesignaciocanlas.workers.dev/checkout"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener"
    >Get the founding rate — $2/mo</a>
    <p class="subscribe-note">
      No extension yet? <a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ckkihjnakpnccnmdipbdibeaibigjjde" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Install Voq first</a> —
      you'll need it to enter your code after checkout.
    </p>
  </div>

  <p class="lockin">
    The founding rate is for early users only. As more people join, the price for
    <strong>new</strong> subscribers rises — on its way to $5/mo. Whatever you lock
    in stays yours <strong>forever</strong>, even after the price moves. Early birds
    win. Actual worms not included.
  </p>

  <section class="activate">
    <h2>How to activate</h2>
    <ol class="steps">
      <li>
        <span class="step-num">1</span>
        <div>
          <h3>Install the Chrome extension</h3>
          <p>Grab Voq from the <a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ckkihjnakpnccnmdipbdibeaibigjjde" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Chrome Web Store</a>. It's free, and this is where your subscription actually gets used — do this first.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="step-num">2</span>
        <div>
          <h3>Subscribe</h3>
          <p>Easiest way: click the key icon inside the Voq panel and choose upgrade — this links your subscription to your browser automatically, so it just activates, no code needed. You can also use the button above; that route hands you a code instead.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="step-num">3</span>
        <div>
          <h3>If you get a code, copy it</h3>
          <p>Only relevant if you subscribed from this page: Stripe's confirmation screen shows a short code. You don't need to memorize it — just copy it.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="step-num">4</span>
        <div>
          <h3>Paste it into Voq</h3>
          <p>Open the Voq panel, click the key icon, paste your code, hit activate. You're unlimited on this device from here on out.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section class="whatyoget">
    <h2>Okay but what am I actually paying for?</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>♾️ No more "you've used your free minutes today"</h3>
        <p>The free tier already includes the natural AI voice — it's capped at a
        generous daily budget. Paid removes the cap entirely, so long articles and
        binge-listening days are never a problem.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>🎧 The same great voice, just unlimited</h3>
        <p>Free or paid, you're hearing the same natural-sounding AI voice, not a
        robotic browser default. Paying doesn't upgrade the voice — it removes the
        leash.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>📑 Skip straight to what you need</h3>
        <p>Voq's panel breaks the page into structure, not just one long ramble —
        jump ahead, skip a section, or rewind, instead of listening to the whole
        thing top to bottom.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>💸 You're funding a tiny, honest project</h3>
        <p>No VC money, no ads, no data broker deals. Just a small tool trying
        to cover its own server bills. Your $2/mo keeps the lights on and
        keeps Voq weird and independent.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="noaccounts">
    <h2>Wait, there's really no sign-up?</h2>
    <p>
      Correct. No email, no password, no "create an account to continue."
      You pay through Stripe's checkout, you get a short code back, you paste
      it into the Voq panel. That's the whole system.
    </p>
    <p>
      Once you've activated a code in Chrome, it just works — it remembers
      itself automatically, even if you uninstall and reinstall the extension,
      as long as you're signed into the same Chrome profile. Get a new
      computer, or want to move it somewhere else entirely? If your old
      device has been quiet for about a week, the code frees itself up
      automatically so you can activate it again elsewhere. No support ticket,
      no "please verify your identity," no email required — because there was
      never one to begin with.
    </p>
    <p class="tiny">
      (One code = one active device at a time, so it can't be shared across a
      dozen people at once — but moving it to your own next laptop is designed
      to just work.)
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <h2>Ready to listen?</h2>
    <p>Install Voq, open any page, and hit play. No account, no credit card
    needed to start.</p>
    <a
      class="install-btn"
      href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ckkihjnakpnccnmdipbdibeaibigjjde"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener"
    >Install Voq — it's free</a>
  </section>

</main>
</div>
</Base>

<style>
  .pricing-page {
    max-width: 880px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 64px 24px 96px;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    color: #0a0a0a;
  }

  .hero { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 56px; }
  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #6b6b6b;
    background: #f4f4f4;
    padding: 6px 12px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 48px);
    line-height: 1.15;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 0 0 18px;
  }
  .hero h1 em { font-style: normal; color: #7c3aed; }
  .hero .sub {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #4b4b4b;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .tiers {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 0 auto 20px;
  }
  .tier {
    border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 28px 20px;
    text-align: center;
    background: #fff;
    transition: transform 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease;
  }
  .tier:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
  .tier.featured {
    border-color: #7c3aed;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(124,58,237,0.12);
  }
  .tier .tag {
    display: block;
    font-size: 10.5px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: #7c3aed;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .tier h2 {
    font-size: 34px;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin: 0 0 6px;
  }
  .tier h2 span { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: #999; }
  .tier .who { font-size: 13px; color: #666; margin: 0; }

  .subscribe-cta {
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 auto 20px;
  }
  .subscribe-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #7c3aed;
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 15px;
    padding: 14px 28px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: opacity 0.15s ease;
  }
  .subscribe-btn:hover { opacity: 0.88; }
  .subscribe-note {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #777;
    margin: 12px 0 0;
  }
  .subscribe-note a { color: #7c3aed; }

  .lockin {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #555;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto 72px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .activate { margin-bottom: 72px; }
  .activate h2 {
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 0 32px;
  }
  .steps {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 auto;
    max-width: 620px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .steps li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .step-num {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #7c3aed;
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 14px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .steps h3 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 4px; }
  .steps p { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: #555; margin: 0; }
  .steps a { color: #7c3aed; }

  .whatyoget { margin-bottom: 72px; }
  .whatyoget h2, .noaccounts h2, .cta h2 {
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 0 32px;
  }
  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .card {
    background: #fafafa;
    border: 1px solid #ececec;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 24px;
  }
  .card h3 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 8px; }
  .card p { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: #555; margin: 0; }

  .noaccounts {
    background: #f8f7ff;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 40px 32px;
    margin-bottom: 72px;
  }
  .noaccounts p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #333;
    max-width: 620px;
    margin: 0 auto 16px;
  }
  .noaccounts .tiny { font-size: 12.5px; color: #888; text-align: center; }

  .cta { text-align: center; }
  .cta p { font-size: 15px; color: #555; max-width: 460px; margin: 0 auto 24px; }
  .install-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #0a0a0a;
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 15px;
    padding: 14px 28px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: opacity 0.15s ease;
  }
  .install-btn:hover { opacity: 0.85; }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
